title: 01.27/21 DPS Hour 2 Carson Palmer

description:
Carson Palmer tells Dan that Aaron Rodgers is not going anywhere. Carson says that Aaron was pissed that the Packer's number 1 draft pick could not help them in the huddle on the field instead of being a quarterback holding a clip board on the sidelines.
